metadata.name: model shoes
metadata.description: One of the things that makes luxury exclusive is the high price tag placed on it. Luxury designs were the norm for the few who could afford them, but now fashion has become attainable on a variety of levels which streetwear excels at. Sportswear brands including Converse, Vans, Nike, or Adidas became essential in the streetwear culture because of their accessibility. The casualness of streetwear that stems from surf, hip-hop, or skater culture contributes to the growing athleisure trend. Wearing casual clothing is seen as fashion-forward and preferable.
